tours.agent: Welcome secret agent to the HQ!|This is the main base of the Penguin Secret Agency.|Here you can find security monitors.|Use these to keep watch over the island.|Make sure to check out the PSA handbook for fresh gear.
tours.attic: This is the Lodge Attic.|It is used to store just about everything!|It also has more Find Four tables.
tours.beach_fair: This is the beach, home of the Lighthouse.| It is a great place to relax in the sun.| Sometimes you can see the pirate ship docked here!
tours.beacon_fair: The Beacon holds the Lighthouse spotlight|and a telescope that you can look through.|And if you thought penguins could not fly|you should try the Jetpack game on the right.
tours.berg_fair: This is the Iceberg.|In the distance you can see our snowy island.|If you want to dive into the ocean depths|try out the Aqua Grabber!
tours.boiler: This is the Boiler Room.|This place is pretty quiet and warm.|Here you can find a filing cabinet with old newspapers.
tours.book: Here is the Book Room.|You can read books from the bookshelf here.|You can also play a game called Mancala.|Read How To Play Mancala before playing.
tours.cave: Here we have the Cave, which has its own pool.|It also has windows to see underwater.|Wait a moment, and a crab may walk by.
tours.cavemine: Here we have the Cave Mine.|Some workers say they've found buried treasure|So grab a hardhat and start digging!
tours.coffee_fair: This is the Coffee Shop.|Here you can grab a hot cup of java.|If you go to the bag of beans in the corner|you can play the game Bean Counters.
tours.cove_fair: Shred some waves at the Cove|Cool off with a swim|or soak up some rays on the beach.
tours.dance_fair: Welcome to the Night Club.|This is THE place for dance parties.|That green puffle on the speaker is called the Keeper.
tours.dock_fair: Welcome to the Dock.|You can play Hydro-Hopper here.|Take a ride on a tube behind the speedboat.
tours.dojo: Welcome to the Dojo.|Here you can play Card-Jitsu.|Only the dedicated will succeed.
tours.dojoext: This is the Dojo Courtyard.|Here you can head to the dojo.|Secrets abound for those who have mastered.|The art of Card-Jitsu.
tours.eco: This is the Recycling Plant!|Throw your recycling into the recycletron 3000|and turn rubbish things into useful things!
tours.esplanade: Welcome to the very scenic Lakeside.|Here you can access the Event Board|where you can find all the upcoming events happening.|That cheerful purple puffle is known as the|Keeper of the Lake.
tours.forest_fair: Here we are at the Forest|It is a great place to enjoy nature.|Go down those stairs to go to the Cove|or explore what lies beneath the large rock.
tours.forts_fair: These forts are for snowball fights.|Some great battles have happened here!|The clock shows Penguin Standard Time.|Hit the target to watch it go crazy!
tours.gadget: Here we have the Gadget Room.|This room holds some of Gary’s most iconic inventions.
tours.garyroom: This is Gary’s Room.|Here you can find Gary’s collection of pins on the wall|As well as some of his famous lab coats.
tours.lake: Wow! This place is the Hidden Lake.|Where did all this treasure come from, I wonder|And it looks like there's a door under the water
tours.light: This is the Lighthouse|the tallest building on the island.|Take a look at the pictures on the wall|or grab a new instrument and perform on stage.|Go upstairs to find the Beacon!
tours.lodge: The Ski Lodge is a great place to warm up.|Or, you can play Find Four with friends.|You can also go Ice Fishing out the back door.
tours.lounge: This is the second floor of the Night Club.|It is called the Arcade.|It is a great place to rest after dancing.|Also, fun arcade games are found here.
tours.mine: Welcome to the Mine|Here you can play Cart Surfer.|Many penguins like playing Cart Surfer for earning coins.|Over there is the Rescue Squad's base of operations|They need your help, and fast!
tours.mtn_fair: Welcome to the Ski Hill!|This is the place to be if you like to sled.|The easiest course is the Bunny Hill.|The hardest is the Ridge Run.
tours.pet: This is the Pet Shop.|Soon you will be able to adopt a pet puffle here.|Play Puffle Roundup by entering the “Employees” door.
tours.pizza: This is the Pizza Parlor.|Come here to order the best pizza.|If you go into the kitchen|you can help make pizzas with the Pizzatron.|Mmm Pizza
tours.plaza_fair: This is the Plaza.|Here you'll find the best pizzeria on the island.|Enter the Stage to experience a wonderful production.
tours.rink_fair: Here we are at the home of football - the Stadium!|Get your buddies together and start a game!|Grab some skates from the Snow and Sports catalog| and join the fun!
tours.shack: Welcome to the Mine Shack!|Head down to the Mine for a game of Cart Surfer|or check out the Recycling Plant beside the beautiful tree.
tours.migrator: This is the pirate ship, the Migrator. Arrrr!|Rockhopper sails the seas in this ship.
tours.shiphold: Here is the ship's cargo hold.|This is where Rockhopper sells his rare items.
tours.quarters: This is the Captain's Quarters!|Rockhopper spends a lot of time here.|Look at the corkboard for his photos!|Or, grab a friend and hunt for some treasure!
tours.shop: This is the Gift Shop.|You can buy clothes from the monthly catalog here.|Colors and backgrounds can be bought as well.|Use coins you have earned from playing minigames.
tours.sport: Welcome to the Sports Shop.|Enter the mysterious curtains for a secret.|But first, you will have to unlock the code!
tours.staff: You have found the Staff Room!|This is where the CPL Team Works.|If you look closely, you can see Ski|floating in space.
tours.stage: Get your tickets!|Here you can experience the featured play on the island.|Check out the costume trunk to get in character.|It's your time to shine!
tours.town_fair: Welcome to the Town!|If the island is having a party|this room is usually well decorated for it.|This is one of the most popular locations on the island.
tours.underwater: BLUB! This place is Underwater|Look at all the colorful fish and plants! And treasure!|This place sure is unusual
tours.village_fair: Here we have the Ski Village|Race down the Ski Hill and chill in the Ski Lodge.

script.name: Monkey King
script.message: The Treasure is so close! In that palace!

script.name: Monkey King
script.message: ... Where the Phoenix Queen Lives!

script.name: Funny Pig
script.message: Um...did you say treasure?

script.name: Monkey King
script.message: Yes! Do you know how to cross this river?

script.name: Funny Pig
script.message: Treasure? Like mud? Anchovies? Chocolate?

script.name: Monkey King
script.message: No... well - maybe. How do we cross?

script.name: Funny Pig
script.message: There is a magic bridge!

script.name: Funny Pig
script.message: First we must find the Golden Feather.

script.name: Monkey King
script.message: Is it close by?

script.name: Funny Pig
script.message: It's hidden in a place of light far away.

script.name: Monkey King
script.message: Lead the way, Funny Pig!

script.name: Monkey King
script.message: Let's search the whole Island together.

script.name: Funny Pig
script.message: Maybe there will be some snacks along the way!

script.name: Monkey King
script.message: We return with the feather!

script.name: Funny Pig
script.message: Hey, that stone just moved!

script.name: Funny Pig
script.message: And I found a Pizza! Candy topping!

script.name: Guardian Dog
script.message: Monkey, this is not your place to be.

script.name: Monkey King
script.message: But I'm not a Monkey. I'm the monkey KING!

script.name: Guardian Dog
script.message: I'm the Guardian Dog! I keep the palace pest free.

script.name: Guardian Dog
script.message: You must prove yourself worthy to enter.

script.name: Monkey King
script.message: Alright... let's see... TURNS TO WIND

script.name: Funny Pig
script.message: Ooh! What's this strange wind?

script.name: Guardian Dog
script.message: Pfft! Don't play games monkey! I know your tricks.

script.name: Monkey King
script.message: But of course. Hey... did you want some snacks?

script.name: Guardian Dog
script.message: Snacks? No! The feather is your key.

script.name: Guardian Dog
script.message: If you found the feather, you may enter.

script.name: Monkey King
script.message: Thank you, Guardian Dog.

script.name: Guardian Dog
script.message: Sure thing, Monkey King! Kai-men-da-ji!

script.name: Phoenix Queen
script.message: Greetings, Monkey! I've been expecting you.

script.name: Monkey King
script.message: Phoenix Queen! It has been a long journey!

script.name: Phoenix Queen
script.message: You are brave and clever!

script.name: Phoenix Queen
script.message: I award you this very rare background.

script.name: Funny Pig
script.message: Wow! Do I get one too?

script.name: Phoenix Queen
script.message: Alright. Just be sure not to gobble it.

script.name: Funny Pig
script.message: Sweet!

script.name: Monkey King
script.message: Thank you, Phoenix Queen...

script.name: Monkey King
script.message: I have enjoyed my adventure.

script.name: Phoenix Queen
script.message: Then you shall have more.

script.name: Director
script.message: Places please!

script.name: Director
script.message: And... action!

script.name: Director
script.message: To enter the palace you need the Golden Feather.

script.name: Director
script.message: Let's take it from the top!

script.name: Director
script.message: Bravo! Fantastic acting!
